00:39:35,120 --> 00:39:37,740
Be prepared.

524
00:39:37,740 --> 00:39:41,820
If it makes you feel better, I can go around a hundred times.

525
00:39:41,820 --> 00:39:45,370
Let's bike it until you feel better.

526
00:39:45,370 --> 00:39:47,340
We're off now.

527
00:39:47,340 --> 00:39:52,450
♫  When I walk this road, it makes me cry  ♫

528
00:39:52,450 --> 00:39:55,380
