00:41:50,190 --> 00:41:54,160
Madam, what is it? Did you see a ghost?

539
00:41:54,160 --> 00:41:55,820
Say something!

540
00:41:55,820 --> 00:41:57,290
Young Gook...

541
00:41:57,290 --> 00:42:03,330
There are snakes in my room! There are snakes in my bed!

542
00:42:05,430 --> 00:42:07,850
Snakes?

543
00:42:12,470 --> 00:42:16,930
These are toys, Madam. Toy snakes.

544
00:42:16,930 --> 00:42:21,450
What? What are these?

545
00:42:21,450 --> 00:42:25,180
These are toy snakes!

546
00:42:25,180 --> 00:42:27,730
Who did this? Who did this!

547
00:42:27,740 --> 00:42:31,760
Did you do it, Lee Se Chan?

548
00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:32,990
No, right?

549
00:42:32,990 --> 00:42:35,670
I did it.

550
00:42:45,650 --> 00:42:50,010
Lee Se Chan. Did you really do that?

551
00:42:50,010 --> 00:42:52,030
Yes.

552
00:42:52,030 --> 00:42:55,610
Lee Se Chan. Why did you do that?

553
00:42:55,610 --> 00:42:59,190
Why did you do such a thing?

554
00:42:59,200 --> 00:43:02,050
Because Grandma was so mean.

555
00:43:02,050 --> 00:43:04,020
What?

556
00:43:04,020 --> 00:43:05,500
What do you mean?

557
00:43:05,500 --> 00:43:07,980
I saw everything!

558
00:43:07,980 --> 00:43:11,470
What did you see?

559
00:43:11,470 --> 00:43:14,640
The person who put that necklace in Ms.Park's drawer

560
00:43:14,640 --> 00:43:16,280
