561
00:43:16,280 --> 00:43:17,660
What?

562
00:43:17,660 --> 00:43:20,660
Grandma hid the necklace in Ms. Park's room,

563
00:43:20,660 --> 00:43:24,500
blamed Ms. Park for stealing it, and made her cry!

564
00:43:24,500 --> 00:43:30,090
That's a bad deed, so that's why I punished Grandma instead of God!

565
00:43:30,090 --> 00:43:34,680
Lee Se Chan. Is everything you said just now true?

566
00:43:34,680 --> 00:43:37,320
Yes! It's all true!

567
00:43:37,320 --> 00:43:40,290
I had short classes today, so I came home early.

568
00:43:40,290 --> 00:43:43,220
And I saw Grandma walking into Ms. Park's room with the necklace

569
00:43:43,220 --> 00:43:45,380
