636
00:47:53,070 --> 00:47:58,910
So please don't take it to heart and forget about it, okay?

637
00:48:01,730 --> 00:48:09,740
Even if anything like that happens, no one in this house thinks you'll do that.

638
00:48:11,860 --> 00:48:16,860
Oh, no, Ms. Park.

639
00:48:19,120 --> 00:48:24,190
It's nothing. I'm really okay.

640
00:48:24,190 --> 00:48:27,410
It's not that...

641
00:48:27,410 --> 00:48:30,130
I'm just very grateful.

642
00:48:30,130 --> 00:48:36,830
I'm so thankful to you for understanding me so well.

643
00:48:36,860 --> 00:48:41,030
Yes, Ms. Park.

644
00:48:45,750 --> 00:48:49,170
It's okay, my daughter.

645
00:48:49,170 --> 00:48:52,810
I'll always be beside you.

646
00:48:54,370 --> 00:48:56,680
Oh.

647
00:49:05,090 --> 00:49:07,040
Hey.

648
00:49:07,040 --> 00:49:10,210
What are you doing out here instead of sleeping?

649
00:49:10,210 --> 00:49:14,200
Mom, why did you come out? Are you unable to sleep as well?

650
00:49:14,200 --> 00:49:18,510
You're right. My heart just keeps beating so fast.

651
00:49:18,510 --> 00:49:22,450
If that Madam and son-in-law Park are really siblings,

652
00:49:22,450 --> 00:49:25,190
