653
00:49:25,190 --> 00:49:30,010
Aren't we going to get punished if we keep pretending that we don't know?

654
00:49:30,010 --> 00:49:33,940
Mom. Should we just try the DNA test?

655
00:49:33,940 --> 00:49:38,570
Yes. If the test says we're wrong, we're wrong.

656
00:49:38,570 --> 00:49:41,990
If it says we're right, we let them meet!

657
00:49:41,990 --> 00:49:47,080
Why don't you go in and pluck a hair from your husband?

658
00:49:47,080 --> 00:49:49,440
Okay.

659
00:50:14,610 --> 00:50:18,610
What are you doing?!

660
00:50:18,610 --> 00:50:21,410
What's going on?

661
00:50:21,460 --> 00:50:24,830
Why are you acting like this?!

662
00:50:24,830 --> 00:50:26,630
Oh, it's not what you think!

663
00:50:26,630 --> 00:50:29,090
I was trying to catch a mosquito,

664
00:50:29,090 --> 00:50:32,970
