665
00:50:34,910 --> 00:50:39,280
- What...
- Go back to sleep.

666
00:51:01,490 --> 00:51:03,150
What?

667
00:51:03,150 --> 00:51:08,040
You acted mad on purpose, Madam?

668
00:51:08,040 --> 00:51:11,810
Then what was I supposed to do? Because of Se Chan, that brat,

669
00:51:11,810 --> 00:51:17,860
