670
00:51:17,860 --> 00:51:21,790
If I hadn't acted crazy, I would have been chased out of this house at that moment!

671
00:51:21,790 --> 00:51:26,030
Even if I hadn't been chased out, how would I live in this house with my head up?

672
00:51:26,030 --> 00:51:28,390
It's embarrassing.

673
00:51:28,390 --> 00:51:30,360
What should we do now, Madam?

674
00:51:30,360 --> 00:51:33,110
The Chairman told me to bring you to the hospital today

675
00:51:33,110 --> 00:51:37,000
