676
00:51:37,000 --> 00:51:39,970
What examination?!

677
00:51:39,970 --> 00:51:42,760
I acted mad, I said!

678
00:51:42,760 --> 00:51:46,090
My goodness.

679
00:52:00,600 --> 00:52:03,000
Chairman Lee! Y-Young Gook!

680
00:52:03,000 --> 00:52:06,130
Ms. Park stole my necklace!

681
00:52:06,130 --> 00:52:10,450
Ms. Park, she's a thieving wench! So kick her out now!

682
00:52:10,450 --> 00:52:13,590
It's really not me...

