713
00:54:11,990 --> 00:54:14,570
I'm more grateful!

714
00:54:14,570 --> 00:54:21,540
Thank you for liking my daughter and giving her such a great opportunity.

715
00:54:26,260 --> 00:54:29,470
Where's my toothbrush?

716
00:54:29,470 --> 00:54:33,270
