748
00:56:30,180 --> 00:56:32,190
I found your older sister!

749
00:56:32,190 --> 00:56:35,280
You're not alone anymore!

750
00:56:35,280 --> 00:56:40,800
Is this really accurate?

751
00:56:40,800 --> 00:56:42,430
Yes!

752
00:56:42,430 --> 00:56:47,350
We tested it using the Madam's toothbrush and your hair!

753
00:56:47,350 --> 00:56:49,840
Where is...

754
00:56:49,840 --> 00:56:54,670
Where is my older sister right now?

755
00:56:56,050 --> 00:56:59,310
Are you...

756
00:56:59,310 --> 00:57:03,810
Are you saying your son-in-law and I are siblings?

757
00:57:03,810 --> 00:57:08,180
What are you talking about it right now?

758
00:57:08,180 --> 00:57:10,610
Are you joking with me?

759
00:57:10,610 --> 00:57:16,610
Oh, why would I? If I do, I will go to hell.

760
00:57:16,610 --> 00:57:19,120
Oh, my goodness.

761
00:57:19,120 --> 00:57:23,280
